EXTRACTED VALUE: A solid and fun, if not deep or terribly rewarding racer - one that ably promotes beauty over brains. [Jan 2006, p.140]
Well, there’s no question Paradise takes Burnout to a whole new level. Is it better though? Personally I’m inclined to think not.
Rainbow Six Vegas might not be the crown jewel of the series, but it's still one of the year's best shooters.
